reviewText: Only in a pinch, will i play this one.
Used this as an introduction to China, and my residents said it was absolutely fascinating -- a great watch!
These acrobats are amazing.  I got to see a live performance of them a number of years ago.  I bought a VHS tape of them and when I saw the DVD I grabbed it.  Just watching them is really amazing.
I don't have any complaints. I thoroughly enjoyed the content, and I thought there was some awesome feats of strength
